article_title: Can Humana Pull Weight Watchers' Fat From The Fire?

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: VideoHealth insurance giant Humana (HUM) and Weight Watchers International (WTW) have partnered to help employers improve worker wellness and battle the nation’s costly obesity epidemic.
